Name: SMF30PNM
Description: Subsystem or product name, for example SMF.

Name: SMF30OSL
Description: Code string for the operating system level to represent the version, release, and modification level as described for CVTPRODN. Guaranteed to be larger in each release.

Name: SMF30SYN
Description: System name (from the SYSNAME parameter in the IEASYSxx parmlib member).

Name: SMF30SYP
Description: Sysplex name (from the SYSPLEX parameter in the COUPLExx parmlib member).
